<div id="pf41a9" class="pf w4b h2f0" data-page-no="41a9"><div class="pc pc41a9 w4b h2f0"><div class="t me7 x71 h5 y1510 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Seek ye first the kingdom of God, </div><div class="t md8 x15 h5 y1e77 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and his righteousness; and all these </div><div class="t m1499 x15 h5 y18ea ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things shall be added unto you&quot; (Matt. </div><div class="t m32f x15 h5 y1e4f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6:33). </div><div class="t m9a3 x71 h35 y1c08 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Those who truly believe that God is </div><div class="t m1a18 x15 h35 y1799 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creator will not worry. The true </div><div class="t m130d x15 h35 y1e71 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">follower of Christ finds among the </div><div class="t m1b8 x15 h35 y2011 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beauties of nature a peace of mind, a </div><div class="t ma99 x15 h35 y18c1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">strength, and a calmness that help to </div><div class="t m798 x15 h35 y10c8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sustain him. Is this not due to the fact </div><div class="t m45a x15 h35 y1f24 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that he sees in the created things his </div><div class="t ma75 x15 h35 y1b60 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavenly Father&apos;s power and ability to </div><div class="t m614 x15 h35 y164e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sustain him? Is this not why Jesus </div><div class="t meb0 x15 h35 y1c09 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pointed </div><div class="t mf6b x6f ha y1e46 ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to </div><div class="t m2bc x59 h35 y1e46 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the things of nature as </div><div class="t me0 x15 h35 y1b46 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evidences of God&apos;s care and reasons </div><div class="t m182 x15 h35 y1d17 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">why we should trust Him? </div><div class="t m3eb x71 h35 y12fa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;All who have chosen God&apos;s service </div><div class="t m7a4 x92 h35 y1ecd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are to rest in His care. Christ pointed </div><div class="t m80 x15 h35 y1a91 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the birds flying in the heavens, to </div><div class="t m864 x15 h35 y1e1d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the flowers of the field, and bade His </div><div class="t m197 x15 h35 y1d51 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hearers consider these objects of </div><div class="t mf35 x15 h35 y1aa3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s creation. &apos;Are not ye of much </div><div class="t m3b8 x15 h35 y1f20 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">more value than they?&apos; He said. Matt. </div><div class="t m78a x92 h35 y1591 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6:26, R.V. The measure of divine </div><div class="t m303 x92 h35 y1f90 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attention, bestowed on &apos;any object is </div><div class="t mce5 x92 h35 y1db5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">proportionate to its rank in the scale of </div><div class="t mbe5 x92 h35 y1be4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">being. The little brown sparrow is </div><div class="t m7ab x15 h35 y19bd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">watched over by Providence. The </div><div class="t me5f x92 h35 y1d07 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">flowers of the field, the grass that </div><div class="t m7c0 x15 h35 y1ee3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">carpets the earth, share the notice and </div><div class="t maa x15 h35 y174a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">care of our heavenly Father. The great </div><div class="t m6c2 x92 h35 y1b18 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Master Artist has taken thought for the </div><div class="t m7e0 x92 h35 y1373 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lilies, making them so beautiful that </div><div class="t ma7a x92 h35 y1e74 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">they outshine the glory of Solomon. </div><div class="t ma93 x92 h35 y1363 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How much more does He care for </div><div class="t m4a6 x92 h35 y649 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man, who is the image and glory of </div><div class="t m425 x92 h35 y1a08 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m61e x35 h35 y1a08 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m6b9 x9e h35 y1a08 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 313. </div><div class="t m170 x71 h35 y1a56 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Since God has done and is doing so </div><div class="t m2dc x92 h35 y1969 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">much for us, it is obvious that we </div><div class="t m587 x92 h35 y1620 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should respond by seeking first &quot;the </div><div class="t mb61 x92 h35 y1b94 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kingdom of God, and his </div><div class="t m2d3 x92 h35 y14fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteousness.&quot; This means that we  </div><div class="t m7df x5a h35 y1510 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">look upon the affairs of this world as </div><div class="t m702 x5a h35 y1e77 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">taking a secondary place in our lives, </div><div class="t m1391 x5a h35 y1b5c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and we devoteevery energy to </div><div class="t m73e x5a h35 y1baa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accomplfshing God&apos;s plans and </div><div class="t meab x5a h35 y1f08 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">purposehfOr us. </div><div class="t m396 x5a h5 y1bf2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x5a h5 y1ab0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m140 x86 h5 y1ab0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His Power to Sustain </div><div class="t m6db x86 h5 y2162 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 6:25) • </div><div class="t m558 x5a h5 y20dd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m142 x86 h5 y20dd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His Carefor His Creatures </div><div class="t m20b x86 h5 y195a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 6:26) </div><div class="t mb7 x5a h5 y1cfb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1199 x86 h5 y1cfb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His &quot;Love of Beauty </div><div class="t mbe7 x86 h5 y1b8a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 6:28-30) </div><div class="t m1ce x5a h5 y1650 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m56f x86 h5 y1d4c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His Provisioniof Work </div><div class="t ma79 x86